'''-{zh-hant:尼古拉斯·約翰·吉布; zh-hk:祈禮勤}-'''（{{lang-en|Nicolas John Gibb}}，{{bd|1960年|9月3日}}），是一位[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]政治人物<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/minister-of-state-for-schools |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-03-09 |archive-date=2017-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170825020742/https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/minister-of-state-for-schools |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/minister-of-state--29 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-03-09 |archive-date=2017-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170824220538/https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/minister-of-state--29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，他的黨籍是[[保守黨_(英國)|保守黨]]。自1997年開始，他擔任[[博格諾里吉斯和利特爾漢普頓_(英國國會選區)|博格諾里吉斯和利特爾漢普頓]]選區選出的英國下議院議員。他在2015年出櫃<ref>{{cite web|last1=Tan|first1=Sylvia|title=UK schools minister Nick Gibb to marry secret partner of 29 years|url=http://www.gaystarnews.com/article/uk-schools-minister-nick-gibb-marry-secret-partner-29-years060615|website=Gay Star News|accessdate=7 June 2015|date=6 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150608003230/http://www.gaystarnews.com/article/uk-schools-minister-nick-gibb-marry-secret-partner-29-years060615|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Watt|first1=Nicholas|title=Nick Gibb, schools minister, to marry partner he kept secret for 29 years|url=http://www.theguardian.com/society/2015/jun/06/nick-gibb-schools-minister-to-marry-partner-he-kept-secret-for-29-years|accessdate=7 June 2015|work=The Guardian|date=6 June 2015|archive-date=2016-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309131955/http://www.theguardian.com/society/2015/jun/06/nick-gibb-schools-minister-to-marry-partner-he-kept-secret-for-29-years|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1997年當選國會議員後便經歷13年的在野政治生涯，曾先後被[[施志安|施志安]]、[[迈克尔·霍华德|迈克尔·霍华德]]、[[戴维·卡梅伦|戴维·卡梅伦]]委任至{{le|官方反對黨前座|Official Opposition frontbench}}任職。自保守黨於2010年上台執政至今，他已在[[英国教育部|教育部]]擔任[[國務大臣_(英國)|國務大臣]]逾八年、任內經歷兩次[[英国首相|首相]]更替。
